{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3716261fe3","title":"在“三一八”纪念晚会上的演讲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d2b1b06bfd","index":0,"year":1939,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"3716261fe3"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"97768e2a79","type":"paragraph","text":"在“三一八”纪念晚会上的演讲口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3716261fe3"},{"id":"55f06e12f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年3月18日）我们要消灭敌人，就要有两种战争：一种是公开的战争，一种是隐款的战争。隐蔽的战争，有战略的进攻，打入故人的内心：也有战略的防御，保卫自己。要打败敌人，须内外夹攻，所以两者都有同样重要的意义。..要求每个保卫工作人员认识这一工作的重要性与光荣性，并希望每个保卫工作人员要有持久性，坚持到抗战的胜利，一直到共产主义的最后胜利11]这是毛泽东出席庆北公学举行的纪念“三一八”案、巴黎公社起","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3716261fe3"}],"page":{"id":"a6fb21d7c3","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3716261fe3","start":268,"end":268}}}},"__N_SSG":true}